Summary: An alien craft hovered over the lake behind my house.

divs: Sighting DetailsIt was dark in october. i was on my computer in my room and i looked outside because i hear a jet engine and i like watching military planes fly over me. but it wasn't a plane. i saw a few large-not very bright lights start to descend behind my house. i heard a slight hum. i ran to my dad in our work out room and told him to look outside. all we saw was an extremely bright light far far away from our house then. I was scared.
